</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Checks if anisotropic filtering is supported on a GPU.    </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x3_d_anisotropic_filtering__set_enabled" kindref="compound">SetEnabled</ref>   </para>
